### PUT - Actualizar noticia
PUT {{api}}/news/REEMPLAZA_CON_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sentiment": "bullish",
  "relevance_score": 0.98
}

###
### DELETE
DELETE {{api}}/news/REEMPLAZA_CON_ID


